      "locked": false,
      "text": "## Diagram\n\n```text\nInternet / Operator Access\nAllowed source: ssh_cidr\nExposed ports: 22, 3000, 9090, 9093\n                 |\n                 v\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| AWS VPC                                                                                          |\n|                                                                                                  |\n|  +------------------------------+                                                                |\n|  | Internet Gateway             |                                                                |\n|  +------------------------------+                                                                |\n|                 |                                                                                |\n|                 v                                                                                |\n|  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |\n|  | Public Subnet (10.0.1.0/24)                                                               |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |  | Public Route Table                   |        | Elastic IP                           |   |  |\n|  |  | 0.0.0.0/0 -> Internet Gateway        |        | Attached to NAT Gateway             |   |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |  | NAT Gateway                          |        | Monitoring Security Group            |   |  |\n|  |  | Public subnet resident               |        | monitoring_sg                       |   |  |\n|  |  | Used for private subnet egress       |        | Ingress: 22, 3000, 9090, 9093      |   |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        | Source: ssh_cidr                    |   |  |\n|  |                                                  | Egress: all outbound                |   |  |\n|  |                                                  +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |  |\n|  |  | Monitoring EC2 Instance                                                             |  |  |\n|  |  | Public IP enabled                                                                   |  |  |\n|  |  |                                                                                    |  |  |\n|  |  | Docker Compose Monitoring Stack                                                    |  |  |\n|  |  |                                                                                    |  |  |\n|  |  |  - Grafana        : 3000                                                           |  |  |\n|  |  |  - Prometheus     : 9090                                                           |  |  |\n|  |  |  - Alertmanager   : 9093                                                           |  |  |\n|  |  |  - Node Exporter  : 9100                                                           |  |  |\n|  |  |                                                                                    |  |  |\n|  |  | Internal service flow                                                              |  |  |\n|  |  |  Grafana      -> Prometheus                                                        |  |  |\n|  |  |  Prometheus   -> Alertmanager                                                      |  |  |\n|  |  |  Prometheus   -> Node Exporter                                                     |  |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |  |\n|  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "## Diagram\n\n```text\nInternet / Operator Access\nAllowed source: ssh_cidr\nExposed ports: 22, 3000, 9090, 9093\n                 |\n                 v\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| AWS VPC                                                                                          |\n|                                                                                                  |\n|  +------------------------------+                                                                |\n|  | Internet Gateway             |                                                                |\n|  +------------------------------+                                                                |\n|                 |                                                                                |\n|                 v                                                                                |\n|  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |\n|  | Public Subnet (10.0.1.0/24)                                                               |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |  | Public Route Table                   |        | Elastic IP                           |   |  |\n|  |  | 0.0.0.0/0 -> Internet Gateway        |        | Attached to NAT Gateway             |   |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |  | NAT Gateway                          |        | Monitoring Security Group            |   |  |\n|  |  | Public subnet resident               |        | monitoring_sg                       |   |  |\n|  |  | Used for private subnet egress       |        | Ingress: 22, 3000, 9090, 9093      |   |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        | Source: ssh_cidr                    |   |  |\n|  |                                                  | Egress: all outbound                |   |  |\n|  |                                                  +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |  |\n|  |  | Monitoring EC2 Instance                                                             |  |  |\n|  |  | Public IP enabled                                                                   |  |  |\n|  |  |                                                                                    |  |  |\n|  |  | Docker Compose Monitoring Stack                                                    |  |  |\n|  |  |                                                                                    |  |  |\n|  |  |  - Grafana        : 3000                                                           |  |  |\n|  |  |  - Prometheus     : 9090                                                           |  |  |\n|  |  |  - Alertmanager   : 9093                                                           |  |  |\n|  |  |  - Node Exporter  : 9100                                                           |  |  |\n|  |  |                                                                                    |  |  |\n|  |  | Internal service flow                                                              |  |  |\n|  |  |  Grafana      -> Prometheus                                                        |  |  |\n|  |  |  Prometheus   -> Alertmanager                                                      |  |  |\n|  |  |  Prometheus   -> Node Exporter                                                     |  |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |  |\n|  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
