      "text": "\nPublic IP enabled\n\nDocker Compose Monitoring Stack\n    - Grafana            : 3000\n    - Prometheus     : 9090\n    - Alertmanager  : 9093\n    - Node Exporter : 9100\n\nInternal service flow\n    - Grafana        -> Prometheus\n    - Prometheus -> Alertmanager\n    - Prometheus -> Node Exporter",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\nPublic IP enabled\n\nDocker Compose Monitoring Stack\n    - Grafana            : 3000\n    - Prometheus     : 9090\n    - Alertmanager  : 9093\n    - Node Exporter : 9100\n\nInternal service flow\n    - Grafana        -> Prometheus\n    - Prometheus -> Alertmanager\n    - Prometheus -> Node Exporter",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
