    {
      "id": "so2hT3fnhGUBGsxrFGeHx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 831.1944444444543,
      "y": -4064.0476190475583,
      "width": 860.9193115234375,
      "height": 1150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b55",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1625146758,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 1453919258,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774964836233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n## Diagram\n\n```text\nNo direct public exposure\nNo public IPs on app instances\nOperational access and monitoring traffic originate from the monitoring host path\n\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| AWS VPC                                                                                          |\n|                                                                                                  |\n|  Referenced dependencies outside the private subnet                                              |\n|                                                                                                  |\n|  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------------+  |\n|  | NAT Gateway                          |        | Monitoring EC2 / monitoring_sg             |  |\n|  | Located in public subnet             |        | Source for SSH and service access          |  |\n|  +--------------------------------------+        | Allowed ports to app instances:            |  |\n|                                                  | 22, 5000, 9100, 8080                       |  |\n|                                                  +--------------------------------------------+  |\n|                                                                                                  |\n|  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |\n|  | Private Subnet (10.0.2.0/24)                                                              |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |  | Private Route Table                  |        | App Security Group                    |   |  |\n|  |  | 0.0.0.0/0 -> NAT Gateway            |        | app_sg                               |   |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        | Ingress: 22 from ssh_cidr            |   |  |\n|  |                                                  | Ingress: 22, 5000, 9100, 8080        |   |  |\n|  |                                                  | Source: monitoring_sg                |   |  |\n|  |                                                  | Egress: all outbound                 |   |  |\n|  |                                                  +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |  | App EC2 Instance 1                  |        | App EC2 Instance 2                  |   |  |\n|  |  | No public IP                        |        | No public IP                        |   |  |\n|  |  |                                    |        |                                    |   |  |\n|  |  | Docker Compose App Stack           |        | Docker Compose App Stack           |   |  |\n|  |  | - Podinfo       : 5000             |        | - Podinfo       : 5000             |   |  |\n|  |  | - Node Exporter : 9100             |        | - Node Exporter : 9100             |   |  |\n|  |  | - cAdvisor      : 8080             |        | - cAdvisor      : 8080             |   |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n```\n\n## Diagram Rules",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\n## Diagram\n\n```text\nNo direct public exposure\nNo public IPs on app instances\nOperational access and monitoring traffic originate from the monitoring host path\n\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| AWS VPC                                                                                          |\n|                                                                                                  |\n|  Referenced dependencies outside the private subnet                                              |\n|                                                                                                  |\n|  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------------+  |\n|  | NAT Gateway                          |        | Monitoring EC2 / monitoring_sg             |  |\n|  | Located in public subnet             |        | Source for SSH and service access          |  |\n|  +--------------------------------------+        | Allowed ports to app instances:            |  |\n|                                                  | 22, 5000, 9100, 8080                       |  |\n|                                                  +--------------------------------------------+  |\n|                                                                                                  |\n|  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |\n|  | Private Subnet (10.0.2.0/24)                                                              |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |  | Private Route Table                  |        | App Security Group                    |   |  |\n|  |  | 0.0.0.0/0 -> NAT Gateway            |        | app_sg                               |   |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        | Ingress: 22 from ssh_cidr            |   |  |\n|  |                                                  | Ingress: 22, 5000, 9100, 8080        |   |  |\n|  |                                                  | Source: monitoring_sg                |   |  |\n|  |                                                  | Egress: all outbound                 |   |  |\n|  |                                                  +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |                                                                                            |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  |  | App EC2 Instance 1                  |        | App EC2 Instance 2                  |   |  |\n|  |  | No public IP                        |        | No public IP                        |   |  |\n|  |  |                                    |        |                                    |   |  |\n|  |  | Docker Compose App Stack           |        | Docker Compose App Stack           |   |  |\n|  |  | - Podinfo       : 5000             |        | - Podinfo       : 5000             |   |  |\n|  |  | - Node Exporter : 9100             |        | - Node Exporter : 9100             |   |  |\n|  |  | - cAdvisor      : 8080             |        | - cAdvisor      : 8080             |   |  |\n|  |  +--------------------------------------+        +--------------------------------------+   |  |\n|  +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+  |\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n```\n\n## Diagram Rules",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
